            . I am a <rs id="t18290611-116-viclabel605" type="occupation">broker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-116-victim905 t18290611-116-viclabel605"></join>, and live in Seymour-street, Euston-square; the prisoner was in my service, and was to receive money on my account, which he was to account for on his return. On the 29th of April he stopped out all night, and sent another lad to do his work. I asked the prisoner if he had received this money; he owned it, and said he had been with a girl, and spent it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290611-116-person906">
                  WILLIAM 
                  PUGH
