                  </persName>
            . I paid the prisoner 12s. 5d. for his master, on the 29th of April, and have his receipt for it.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written defence, stating that the prosecutor had offered to give up the prosecution, and take the amount by instalments.</p>
               <p>
            
